    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained throughout its ownership. The exterior retains a strong shine, though you will find some minor stone chips on the hood and a few light surface scratches consistent with regular use. Inside, the cabin is clean and comfortable, with only slight wear on the driver's seat bolster and primary touchpoints. Mechanically, it runs smoothly and all features are fully functional, making it a dependable choice for its next owner.",
