    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant work to be roadworthy. The engine currently runs very roughly, exhibits a noticeable knocking sound, and there are several active fluid leaks underneath. The exterior has multiple deep scratches, faded paint, and some rust spots on the rocker panels, while the interior shows heavy wear with torn upholstery and a lingering musty odor. This car is ideal for someone looking for a major project or a source of parts, as it is being sold strictly as-is.",
