    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this superlative example, maintained to an exacting standard that mirrors its original showroom delivery. The vehicle exhibits a flawless aesthetic and mechanical profile, representing a rare acquisition for the discerning collector or enthusiast. Every surface and component reflects a commitment to preservation, ensuring an ownership experience that is indistinguishable from new.",
